description: An optional set of parameters corresponding to transactions options.

start_date.description: The earliest date for which to fetch transaction history. Dates should be formatted as YYYY-MM-DD.

end_date.description: The most recent date for which to fetch transaction history. Dates should be formatted as YYYY-MM-DD.

days_requested.description: The maximum number of days of transaction history to request for the Transactions product.
